                                       Notes:
                                      -======-


 Appropriately titled - Amsterdam Trance Classics - is all about bringing
 back some of our classic Trance moments in an attentive glorious 2014
 Remastering! We have been digging through all our old dat tapes in order to
 find all our original master tapes of some of our Classic Recordings through
 the years and restore them to fit all the new media formats. We are proud to
 present to you our fifth reissue in the shape of Armin van Buuren presents
 Perpetuous Dreamer with the massive single "Future Funland", in 7 mixes
 through the years. Included are the original mix, as well as remixes by
 Astura, Gate 42 and DJ Alici.
